extends ../default

block content
  h1 Delete User

  p Make sure you know what you're doing here.

  p The user to delete is:

  strong= user

  p When you click the button below, you will delete this user forever.

  form(method="POST")
    input(type="hidden" name="user" value="#{user}") 
    input(type="submit" name="submit" value="Delete User Forever")